@startuml
|Match Management|
start
:Select a field and a slot;
:Submit POST /v1/fields/{field_id}/reservations;
|Field Management|
:Check that the field is active;
:Check start_at < end_at;
:Check that no active overlap exists;
if (Validation OK?) then (yes)
  :Create the reservation;
  :Publish FieldReservationCreated;
  :Return 201;
else (no)
  :Return 400 or 409;
endif
stop
@enduml
